<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{#if lang}}{{lang}}{{else}}fr{{/if}}">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>{{#eq lang "en"}}FASO DIGITALISATION — Account recovery{{else}}FASO DIGITALISATION — Récupération de votre compte{{/eq}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f3f6f4;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f6f4;padding:32px 0;">
    <tr><td align="center">
      <table width="640" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#ffffff;padding:28px 32px;">
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;">FASO DIGITALISATION</h1>
            <p style="margin:6px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#FFD700;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Account recovery — magic link{{else}}Récupération de compte — lien magique{{/eq}}
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:32px;color:#222;">
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Hello{{else}}Bonjour{{/eq}}{{#if userFirstName}} <strong>{{userFirstName}}</strong>{{/if}},
            </p>
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}You requested to recover your FASO administrator account. Click the button below to start the recovery process. This link is <strong>valid for {{expiresInMinutes}} minutes</strong> and is <strong>single-use</strong>.{{else}}Vous avez demandé la récupération de votre compte administrateur FASO. Cliquez sur le bouton ci-dessous pour démarrer la procédure. Ce lien est <strong>valide {{expiresInMinutes}} minutes</strong> et <strong>à usage unique</strong>.{{/eq}}
            </p>

            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:28px 0;">
              <tr><td align="center">
                <a href="{{recoveryLink}}" style="display:inline-block;background:#1b5e20;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:6px;border:2px solid #1b5e20;">
                  {{#eq lang "en"}}Recover my account{{else}}Récupérer mon compte{{/eq}}
                </a>
              </td></tr>
            </table>

            <p style="font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.5;text-align:center;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}If the button does not work, copy this URL into your browser:{{else}}Si le bouton ne fonctionne pas, copiez cette URL dans votre navigateur :{{/eq}}<br/>
              <span style="font-family:monospace;color:#1b5e20;word-break:break-all;">{{recoveryLink}}</span>
            </p>

            <table width="100%" style="margin:28px 0 12px;border-collapse:collapse;background:#f9f9f9;border-radius:6px;">
              <tr><td style="padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:12px;color:#666;width:35%;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Source IP{{else}}Adresse IP source{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;font-family:monospace;">{{ipAddress}}</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px 14px;font-size:12px;color:#666;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}User agent{{else}}Navigateur{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px 14px;font-size:12px;font-family:monospace;color:#444;">{{userAgent}}</td></tr>
            </table>

            <div style="background:#fff3e0;border:2px solid #E53935;border-radius:8px;padding:18px 22px;margin-top:24px;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#b71c1c;line-height:1.5;">
                <strong>{{#eq lang "en"}}Security warning{{else}}Avertissement sécurité{{/eq}}</strong> &mdash;
                {{#eq lang "en"}}If you did not initiate this request, <strong>ignore this message</strong> and immediately change your password. Then contact <a href="mailto:security@faso.bf" style="color:#b71c1c;">security@faso.bf</a>.{{else}}Si vous n'êtes pas à l'origine de cette demande, <strong>ignorez ce message</strong> et changez immédiatement votre mot de passe. Contactez ensuite <a href="mailto:security@faso.bf" style="color:#b71c1c;">security@faso.bf</a>.{{/eq}}
              </p>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#FFD700;padding:14px 32px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;">
            FASO DIGITALISATION — République du Burkina Faso<br/>
            <a href="https://faso.bf/security" style="color:#FFD700;text-decoration:underline;">https://faso.bf/security</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
